      "content": "got it. so it's a mix of physical texture and chemical stuff. i was thinking though, it's kind of weird to imagine all that strength and all those structural components just sitting there hidden under the surface in the dark. is there anything else that happens inside the concrete once it's poured that we don't see from the outside?",
